It's just water.

6
00:01:24,367 --> 00:01:26,870
It's a lot of water.

7
00:01:26,870 --> 00:01:27,837
A lot of...

8
00:01:27,837 --> 00:01:28,838
(RETCHING)

9
00:01:32,008 --> 00:01:33,343
Come on.

10
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,902
You okay, boss?

11
00:01:59,402 --> 00:02:01,287
Yeah, I'm fine
, I just...

12
00:02:01,287 --> 00:02:04,290
I just can't...
Can't stomach the water.

13
00:02:07,877 --> 00:02:09,379
You're my new partner.

14
00:02:09,379 --> 00:02:11,881
That's right.

15
00:02:11,881 --> 00:02:14,884
Not the best way to meet,
with my head halfway
