the man, the legend,"

17
00:02:17,921 --> 00:02:18,922
I'll give you that.

18
00:02:18,922 --> 00:02:20,390
?
The legend

19
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:21,391
What the hell
you boys smoking

20
00:02:21,391 --> 00:02:23,393
over there
in Portland, anyway?

21
00:02:23,393 --> 00:02:26,596
Seattle. I came from
the office in Seattle.

22
00:02:29,599 --> 00:02:31,601
How long you been
with the Marshals?

23
00:02:31,601 --> 00:02:33,102
Four years.

24
00:02:34,604 --> 00:02:37,106
So you know
how small it is.

25
00:02:37,607 --> 00:02:39,275
Sure.

26
00:02:39,275 --> 00:02:42,278
What about you?
You got a girl? Married?

27
00:02:43,279 --> 00:02:44,581
I was.

28
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:51,004
(INAUDIBLE)

29
