(WAVES ROARING)

30
00:02:56,876 --> 00:02:57,877
She died.

31
00:02:58,878 --> 00:03:00,129
Jesus. I don't...

32
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:03,132
Don't worry about it.

33
00:03:03,132 --> 00:03:06,636
There was a fire
at the apartment building
while I was at work.

34
00:03:06,636 --> 00:03:08,638
Four people died.

35
00:03:08,638 --> 00:03:10,139
It was the smoke
that got her,
not the fire.

36
00:03:10,139 --> 00:03:12,141
See, that's important.

37
00:03:12,642 --> 00:03:14,027
I'm sorry, boss.

38
00:03:14,027 --> 00:03:16,863
?
Where are my
goddamn cigarettes

39
00:03:16,863 --> 00:03:19,282
Oh, here,
have one of mine.

40
